117
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:32,310
Okay.

118
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:37,030
Chief Xue.

119
00:06:37,909 --> 00:06:39,510
Thank you for your guidance.

120
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:40,540
Goodbye.

121
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:47,110
