132
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,430
Master.

133
00:07:14,350 --> 00:07:15,150
Don't worry.

134
00:07:15,590 --> 00:07:16,700
I will find all five herbs

135
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:17,830
