148
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:45,230
It’s just that I've been

149
00:07:45,710 --> 00:07:47,370
busy with matters in the sect.

150
00:07:49,990 --> 00:07:50,850
No matter what,

151
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,740
